      "text": "POST   /api/auth/signup\nPOST   /api/auth/signin\nPOST   /api/auth/signout\n GET   /api/auth/me       → returns current session user\n\n GET   /api/qrcodes       → list all QR codes for user\nPOST   /api/qrcodes       → create & save a new QR code\n DEL   /api/qrcodes/[id]  → delete a QR code by id\n\nPOST   /api/upload        → upload image, return URL\nPOST   /api/chat          → streaming AI assistant",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "POST   /api/auth/signup\nPOST   /api/auth/signin\nPOST   /api/auth/signout\n GET   /api/auth/me       → returns current session user\n\n GET   /api/qrcodes       → list all QR codes for user\nPOST   /api/qrcodes       → create & save a new QR code\n DEL   /api/qrcodes/[id]  → delete a QR code by id\n\nPOST   /api/upload        → upload image, return URL\nPOST   /api/chat          → streaming AI assistant",
